original_text:
p = -5:0.01:5;
hold on
plot(p,real(log(p)),"b")
plot(p,imag(log(p)),"r")
xticks(-5:5)
xlabel("Price (p)")
ylabel("Ordinate")
legend(["real(log(p))" "imag(log(p))"],AutoUpdate=false)
grid minor
